description:
This is a totally new tab that I made sometime ago, UVERworld lacks good tabs so I made this one when I was bored c:
Okay, the guitar parts seems to be ok to me, although I'm not a drummer the drums seems fine too, the bass isn't so accurate because I have a bad headphone to listen well the bassline (and I was a bit lazy when I was in the bass track xD), strings and other effects seems good too...
Tempo changings are OK, the panning isn't so accurated, my pc has a messed up sound configuration, I was not sure about what I was doing in the tab when I was configuring the pannings because of that...
Well, any corrections are welcome if you find some error xD
xD
